We reproduced and extended the rate-based system model of the circuit that was published in a previous publication32. The circuit is described as a rate model with a connection matrix derived from the larva connectome. Each neuron population (mechano-ch, iLNa, iLNb, fbLN-Ha, and fLN-Hb) was modeled by a single node (Fig. 3h-p). The dynamics read:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
